    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piczle Cross Adventure is Score Studios's critically acclaimed 2D logic-puzzle adventure. This content pack takes all the nonogram puzzles from this game and makes them available to play in Piczle World of Puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294140/extras/031616e7e9783a39176a8c55d0688016.avif?t=1766800878\" width=404 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All 320 original puzzles, including the 12 collage puzzles, are here, as well as 10 extra puzzles, including one collage puzzle, from the free demo and the 20 secret unlockable puzzles from the original game, making a grand total of 354 individual nonogram logic-puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294140/extras/8474ae15b83f2ae3c4f856e80c6c253f.avif?t=1766800878\" width=656 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On top of that you'll get the Piczle Cross Adventure profile background, character avatars and sticker! (<i>NOTE: these items are also available to owners of the original game on Steam!</i>)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294140/extras/f7dac165769ecd9fc6f5eadd3cbfa41f.avif?t=1766800878\" width=371 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And finally, the Piczle Cross Adventure puzzle theme! You can play any puzzle in Piczle World of Puzzle using the graphics and backgrounds of the original game, or add it to your random rotation of puzzle themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please note: </strong>This DLC <u>only</u> contains the puzzles from Piczle Cross Adventure. For the full award-winning story-driven experience please play the original game.</p>",
